<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Business Compliance Services - Greymatter Accountancy</title>
  <link class="stylesheet" rel="stylesheet" href="../css/styles.css">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=Sora:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/header', { rootPath: '../', currentPage: 'page' }) %>

  <section class="page-header page-header-light">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Business Compliance Services</h1>
      <p>Professional, reliable compliance reporting to keep your UK business on solid footing with HMRC & Companies House.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="services-detail services-page">
    <div class="container">
      
      <div class="services-grid" style="margin-bottom: 40px;">
        
        <!-- Bookkeeping -->
        <div class="service-detail-card">
          <div class="service-detail-header">
            <div class="service-detail-icon"><i class="fas fa-book"></i></div>
            <h2>Bookkeeping</h2>
          </div>
          <div class="service-detail-content">
            <p>Accurate, real-time records are the foundation of healthy business decisions. We maintain daily, weekly, or monthly ledgers so your accounts are always audit-ready.</p>
            <h3>What we cover:</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>Sales and purchase ledger updates</li>
              <li>Bank, credit card, and loan reconciliations</li>
              <li>Receipt processing via cloud tools (Dext, Hubdoc)</li>
              <li>Monthly management reporting support</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Statutory Accounts -->
        <div class="service-detail-card">
          <div class="service-detail-header">
            <div class="service-detail-icon"><i class="fas fa-shield-halved"></i></div>
            <h2>Statutory Accounts</h2>
          </div>
          <div class="service-detail-content">
            <p>Year-end financial statements prepared in strict accordance with UK GAAP (FRS 102/105) and filed directly with Companies House and HMRC.</p>
            <h3>What we cover:</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>Balance Sheets and Income Statements</li>
              <li>Full notes and director reports preparation</li>
              <li>Reconciliation of balance sheet control accounts</li>
              <li>E-filing submissions to Companies House</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Payroll & Pensions -->
        <div class="service-detail-card">
          <div class="service-detail-header">
            <div class="service-detail-icon"><i class="fas fa-people-carry-box"></i></div>
            <h2>Payroll & Pensions</h2>
          </div>
          <div class="service-detail-content">
            <p>Pay your team correctly, securely, and on time. We handle the complete monthly or weekly payroll bureau cycle, including pension compliance.</p>
            <h3>What we cover:</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>Real Time Information (RTI) submissions to HMRC</li>
              <li>Custom payslip generation and distribution</li>
              <li>Auto-enrolment workplace pension compliance (NEST, etc.)</li>
              <li>P60s, P45s, and student loan deduction management</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- VAT Returns -->
        <div class="service-detail-card">
          <div class="service-detail-header">
            <div class="service-detail-icon"><i class="fas fa-receipt"></i></div>
            <h2>VAT Returns</h2>
          </div>
          <div class="service-detail-content">
            <p>Stay aligned with Making Tax Digital (MTD) rules. We compute, double-check, and file your VAT returns, choosing the most optimal schemes.</p>
            <h3>What we cover:</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>VAT return preparation and MTD-compliant filing</li>
              <li>Scheme assessment (Cash, Accrual, Flat Rate, Annual)</li>
              <li>Partial exemption calculations and advice</li>
              <li>HMRC VAT audit representation and queries</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Corp Tax -->
        <div class="service-detail-card">
          <div class="service-detail-header">
            <div class="service-detail-icon"><i class="fas fa-percent"></i></div>
            <h2>Corp Tax</h2>
          </div>
          <div class="service-detail-content">
            <p>Ensure your company files accurate CT600 forms. We analyze your expenses and capital spending to optimize tax reliefs and allowances.</p>
            <h3>What we cover:</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>Corporation Tax computation and CT600 preparation</li>
              <li>Capital Allowance claims (Section 198, AIA, Super-deductions)</li>
              <li>R&D tax relief review and submission</li>
              <li>Quarterly installment payment plans if applicable</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Secretarial & HMRC -->
        <div class="service-detail-card">
          <div class="service-detail-header">
            <div class="service-detail-icon"><i class="fas fa-file-contract"></i></div>
            <h2>Secretarial & HMRC</h2>
          </div>
          <div class="service-detail-content">
            <p>Handle corporate administration without the stress. We act as your company secretarial department and manage all formal correspondence with HMRC.</p>
            <h3>What we cover:</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>Annual Confirmation Statement filing</li>
              <li>Registered Office and Director details management</li>
              <li>Resolving HMRC compliance and billing discrepancies</li>
              <li>Share transfer forms and dividend declarations</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Need Comprehensive Business Compliance?</h2>
      <p>Let's design a structured compliance package for your company.</p>
      <a href="../index.html#contact" class="btn btn-primary">Book a Consultation</a>
    </div>
  </section>
  <%- include('partials/footer', { rootPath: '../', currentPage: 'page' }) %>
</body>
</html>
